      <h3><a class="anchor" id="top" name="hall"></a>Trinity Mid-whitgiftian Hall now available for hire</h3>
      <p>Now available for hire: The Clubhouse at Trinity Sanderstead Sports and Social Club is set in tranquil surroundings, overlooking playing fields at the end of Lime Meadow Avenue. With a large free car park and its proximity to bus routes, it is the perfect venue for classes and clubs, rehearsals, parties, wakes, sporting events and business meetings. If you are interested in hiring The Clubhouse for a function or a regular booking please call 07582 910094 or email <%= mail_to "admin@tsssc.co.uk" %></p>

      <h3><a class="anchor" id="top" name="Plan"></a>Croydon Council's "Croydon Plan", consultation meetings</h3>
      <p>Croydon Council has produced a multi page plan which is available online, <%= link_to "on this link", "https://www.croydon.gov.uk/sites/default/files/articles/downloads/Croydon%20Local%20Plan%20-%20Detailed%20Policies%20and%20Proposals%20%28Preferred%20and%20Alternative%20Options%29.pdf" %> detailing their proposals for the future management of Croydon and it's environment. <%= link_to "Consultation meetings are ongoing", "/resource/croydon_plan_meetings.pdf" %>. The nearest to Sanderstead will be on Tuesday 8th December at 3.30 and 8 pm at Purley Baptist Church.</p>


